    <h1>About the Operator</h1>
    <p class="static-page__lang-switch"><a href="https://freelife50.com/profile/">このページを日本語で読む</a></p>
    <p>Ramen, Beer & Blog is a personal blog run by Hiroshi, a blogger in his 50s. The site records everyday life, ramen, beer, walking, hiking, time with the Shiba Inu Momiji, side work, and thoughts from life after 50.</p>

    <h2>Operator</h2>
    <p>Hiroshi</p>

    <h2>Site Name</h2>
    <p>Ramen, Beer & Blog</p>

    <h2>Site URL</h2>
    <p><a href="https://freelife50.com/">https://freelife50.com/</a></p>

    <h2>Editorial Policy</h2>
    <p>The blog is written as honestly as possible based on real experiences, research, and thoughts that come with life in one's 50s. Rather than making definitive statements as an expert, the goal is to write articles that help readers of the same generation pause and think a little.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Please see the <a href="https://en.freelife50.com/contact/">Contact page</a>.</p>
